{"342","","Grants a full red heart container.#+0.7 Tears up.#-0.16 Shot speed down."},
{"343","","Grants 1 soul heart.#+1 Luck up.#Spawns 2 keys.#Rare chance to spawn a golden key instead of a regular key."},
